      "severity": "High",
      "location": "getOrderHistory, function parameters",
      "reproduction": "Call getOrderHistory('cust-1', -1, 10) → OFFSET = -10, Postgres error. Call getOrderHistory('cust-1', 1, 999999) → attempts to load ~1M rows into memory.",
